"uid":231402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"由6月12射催淚彈到依家 香港人都習慣咁<br />\n呢啲唔可以習慣㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccfb5aea38b10c8336ae7aac637dab17cb04bd9","tid":1563340,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:14:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"af6a96cc600591713b200dac217446bad1ad67a9","tid":1563340,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"好嬲 完"},{"pid":"28a2f8824ae3857ffca94a9686a464e0706a4fca","tid":1563340,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n［重要］外媒讚我地玩人鏈唱國歌式抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼￼<br />\n我係香港人呀屌￼￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人繼續自high 啦 又比d 掌聲自己<br />\n屌你地老母 ￼<br />\n出面行動post 又唔見你地推得咁落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n十幾個國歌post ￼Twitter 又全部國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺義士呢？￼<br />\nTwitter 我search #sanukling （唔係#sunukling) 得少量post 咩事<br />\n大家可唔可以宣傳下新屋嶺義士被打強姦情況<br />\n引起國際關注￼<br />\n唔好比義士成為condom￼ <br />\n唔好比佢地既血白流<br />\n新屋嶺系核彈 港版集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界今晚集中火力 tag #sanukling # Chinazi #xinjiang #policestate #warcrime￼ <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家人權法唔系100%通過￼<br />\n可以加辣亦可以減辣<br />\n之前就受害者模式<br />\n依家就勝利者模式唱國歌<br />\n你估依家美國會唔會幫你加辣￼￼￼<br />\n未通過之前好心大家扮下野啦 ￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續唱美國國歌 揮美國國旗<br />\n同埋做好文宣 咩都好形造到我地有幾慘得幾慘￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f1c6514a43a63e427cf2f98a24ccaa4bd045a2","tid":1563340,"uid":255816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"每星期全民文宣日 大家齊來貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563334</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思借個位宣傳<br />\n一齊每個禮拜貼文宣啦！<br />\n唔好輕視文宣重要性<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b8afd937b2b9101900c46c0850717c951b52ec","tid":1563340,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af6a96cc600591713b200dac217446bad1ad67a9","tid":1563340,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"好嬲 完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:18:06.000Z","msg":"港豬下場或者該當如此<br />\n比黑警迫害完一個又一個<br />\n細路都唔放過<br />\n港豬得個嬲字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人提出升級同方法<br />\n又會有人屌佢 咁你又唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如是者 原地踏步"},{"pid":"14e92cd809aad4c11be2afd56ae54f3f59a61c33","tid":1563340,"uid":267461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"悲但真⋯"},{"pid":"e0141fc50d55235a233d02e5605b00db4c0f5356","tid":1563340,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:29:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}